re that fosters your professional growth and development  we invite you to search our current openings and review the process for submitting applications recruitment fraud alert amerisourcebergen has been made aware of recruitment scams for offers of employment that are not authorized on behalf of the company or made by a company representative amerisourcebergen has a formal application process and will not conduct interviews through email instant messenger google hangout or other internet chat platforms during the application process amerisourcebergen does not request or solicit money bank information tax forms or credit card information amerisourcebergen does not require applicants to purchase equipment or software amerisourcebergen does not communicate with applicants using text messaging instant messenger or google hangout if you have concerns that your offer of employment may be fraudulent or you have been a victim of this type of crime please contact  you may also report this crime to the fbis internet crime complaint center for investigation httpwwwicgovdefaultaspx as well as the federal trade commission ftc wwwftccomplaintassistantgov   search jobs how to apply we have a variety of positions available for all different levels of education skills and experience after you find a position that aligns with your qualifications please complete the online application process and submit your resume electronically when your application is successfully submitted you will receive an electronic acknowledgement should you be selected to interview for a position one of our talent acquisition specialists will contact you as part of our employment process all new hires must successfully complete a preemployment background check that includes a criminal history check employment verification education verification and drug screening additional checks may be required depending on the position requirements internships the amerisourcebergen summer internship program offers students the opportunity to gain valuable realworld business experience and make a meaningful contribution in a teamoriented environment students can expect to be challenged and feel connected and valued by the amerisourcebergen community key components of the summer internship experience industry knowledge learn about the different businesses at amerisourcebergen our customers vendors and patients professional development attend workshops webinars and training sessions to enhance your foundational skills networking interact with senior leaders to learn about their career paths elements for success and advice to help prepare you for your career interns also have the opportunity to network formally and informally with associates in their department location and business unit teambuilding partner with other interns and associates to develop new professional relationships give back to the communities we serve and be part of a team committed to patients customers and each other requirements to be considered for the program candidates must possess a minimum cumulative gpa of  enrolled as a fulltime undergraduate student at a fouryear institution be a rising sophomore junior or senior able to commit to the program timeframe have us citizenship or lawful permanent resident status copyright   amerisourcebergen corporation all rights reserved amerisourcebergen  contact amerisourcebergen knowledgedriven what it takes home  contact contact thank you for your interest were ready to answer any questions you may have corporate headquarters  morris drive chesterbrook pa  mailing address po box  valley forge pa  phone number  email address solutionsamerisourcebergencom general inquiry or feedback name email company region subject message topic general news  media careers investor relations customer care customer inquiry services  solutions required field message copyright   amerisourcebergen corporation all rights reserved amerisourcebergen  pharmacies amerisourcebergen knowledgedriven 